casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Maurer.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Maurer (1996), 75 Ohio St.3d 1207.]

(No. 96-486 Decided March 27, 1996.)

The resignation as an attorney of Earl Hoak Maurer of Columbus, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0006694, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur. Submitted March 20, 1996
